name: CheetahMen II: The Lost Levels
description:
CheetahMen II: The Lost Levels is a redoing of CheetahMen II that corrects the various glitches so now the entire game is playable. The game is available in two packages.

The Ultimate Collector Package contains:
  • Two games with two dustcovers and two boxes. One is factory sealed so as to save as a collectable, the other is to play. One is in a red cartridge, the other is in a clear cartridge.
  • A theater size poster of 24" by 36".
  • CheetahMix music CD
  • CheetahMen: The Creation comic book
  • CheetahMen II: The Lost Levels guidebook
  • A "Blame Me" Lost Levels T-shirt
The Players Set contains:
  • A blue game cartridge, a dustcover and a box
  • A "Blame Me" Lost Levels T-shirt
  • CheetahMen: The Creation comic book
  • CheetahMen II: The Lost Levels guide book
All the games in both sets are hologram serial numbered and a limited edition.
